DA Federal Council Chairperson nominations closed The Democratic Alliance (DA) can announce that the submissions for nominations for Chairperson of the Federal Council closed at 17:00 this afternoon. The election for the position will take place towards the end of October at Federal Council. I am pleased to announce the following experienced individuals who have availed themselves for this position: Trollip, Athol Walters, Thomas Waters, Mike Zille, Helen The DA trusts that this will be a constructive period of campaigning and contestation of ideas between the candidates in line with our values of Freedom, Fairness, Opportunity and Diversity. Statement issued by Desiree Van Der Walt - Presiding Officer of Federal Council Elections, 4 October 2019